691
00:44:46,967 --> 00:44:50,494
They sound like spoken words.
As in Type 8...

692
00:44:50,671 --> 00:44:54,072
...the good-luck sneeze.

693
00:44:54,241 --> 00:44:55,606
Horseshoe!

